Meet <b>Austin</b>, our featured citizen of the week!<br><br>Austin has been living at his <a href='/home/?user=austisport'>84545 Timberwolf Way</a> residence in Metro Park, since February 12th, 2006. <br><br>Austin loves living in Metro Park. It's one of Millsberry's newest and hippest neighborhoods, and close to tons of entertainment because it's located in the heart of downtown.<br><br>Austin describes himself as very athletic, a little creative, and smart. Sounds like the perfect combination for a Millsberry citizen.<br><br>His interests include basketball, animals, and computers. Guess he should have no problem surfing the net to check sports scores while listening to his favorite band and horsing around.<br><br>If you're looking for Austin, your best bets are the Amusement Park, the Arcade, or the Zoo. He's all about entertainment so, if he's got free time, he's likely to be hanging out at one of these hot spots.<br><br>If you happen to see Austin, make sure you shake his hand and thank him for being such an outstanding citizen!<br></div>
